--[[
    Blitz  •  V2.1  •  Asuneteric
    ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
    Changes in V2.1
    ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
    WEBHOOK
      • Queued send system — outbound embeds are batched through a
        consumer task so Discord's rate-limits are never hit blindly
      • Automatic retry (up to 3 attempts) with exponential back-off;
        HTTP 429 Retry-After header is respected
      • Richer embed: server JobId field, Game PlaceId, live bubble
        size from leaderstats, shiny badge in title
      • "Send Test Embed" button — verifies URL before farming
      • Per-identity cooldown (petName+rarity key) instead of relying
        on a Frame attribute that can be recycled by the game's UI pool
      • Mythic filter toggle was missing from FilterSection — added

    BUG FIXES
      • 4x Egg Sniper pattern used (?i) regex syntax which Lua does not
        support — replaced with a proper Lua string.lower() + gsub
      • Duplicate Egg Teleport UI section (was built twice, under both
        Tabs.World and later Tabs.World again) — consolidated
      • Auto-Collect: removed client-side inst:Destroy() which could
        cause desyncs; replaced with a parent-check guard

    LOGIC / PERFORMANCE
      • Potion loop: first activation fires the remote immediately
        (no initial 30-min wait) by seeding lastUsed to 0
      • State table is now the single source of truth — all loops
        read from Options once per iteration and write to State,
        avoiding repeated Options lookups inside hot loops
      • Auto-Delete continuous sweep now exits early if the toggle
        is turned off mid-sweep, preventing zombie delete chains
      • Container blacklist extended to cover "orb", "coin", "gem"
        false-positive prefixes that appeared in some egg area folders
      • Memory cleanup timer reduced to 30 s (was 60 s) to keep the
        UUID table small on heavy collect sessions
    ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
]]

